Supreme Court, Appellate Term, February, 1897.

Before Daly, P. J., McAdam and Bischoff, JJ

Joseph M. Biggert, Respondent, v. Edwin Nichols, Appellant. Appeal from an order of the General Term of the City Court dismissing an appeal from order of Special Term. J. B. Sabine, for Appellant; Cardozo & Nathan, for Respondent.

Appeal dismissed, with costs, upon argument.
